-- Saints Beat Cowboys 30-27 in 2nd NFL Thanksgiving Day Game; Patriots Win
-- B y   D a n   B a y n e s
-- 2010-11-26T01:08:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-26/saints-beat-cowboys-30-27-in-2nd-nfl-thanksgiving-day-game-patriots-win.html
The New Orleans Saints beat the
Dallas Cowboys 30-27 in the second U.S. Thanksgiving Day
National Football League game.   Tom Brady earlier threw for four second-half touchdowns and
341 yards as the New England Patriots defeated the Detroit Lions
45-24. The New York Jets host the Cincinnati Bengals tonight.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
